      "type": "conversation",
      "title": "Conversation Practice 1（会話）: The Windy Day",
      "context": "Talking about the weather.",
      "lines": [
        {
          "spk": "A",
          "jp": "今日は 風が 強いですね。",
          "en": "The wind is strong today, isn't it?",
          "terms": [
            "v_kyou",
            "v_kaze",
            "v_tsuyoi"
          ]
        },
        {
          "spk": "B",
          "jp": "はい。強風ですから、電車が 来ません。",
          "en": "Yes. Because of the strong wind, the train is not coming.",
          "terms": [
            "v_kyoufuu",
            "v_densha",
            { "id": "v_kuru", "form": "polite_masen" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "spk": "A",
          "jp": "えっ、そうですか。何で 帰りますか。",
          "en": "Eh, is that so? How (by what) will you go home?",
          "terms": [
            "k_nani",
            { "id": "v_kaeru", "form": "polite_masu" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "spk": "B",
          "jp": "車で 帰ります。",
          "en": "I will go home by car.",
          "terms": [
            "k_kuruma",
            { "id": "v_kaeru", "form": "polite_masu" }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
