        {
          "spk": "B",
          "jp": "はい。でも、日本語は むずかしいですね。",
          "en": "Yes. But Japanese is difficult.",
          "terms": [
            "v_nihongo",
            "v_muzukashii"
          ]
        },
        {
          "spk": "A",
          "jp": "そうですね。私は 少し 弱気です。",
          "en": "That's right. I am a little faint-hearted (discouraged).",
          "terms": [
            "v_sukoshi",
            "v_yowaki"
